================================

DEFINITIONS

================================

fn_post_custom_fields.php
	Adds a custom field to the Post the author can check to indicate the post contains an infographic. This triggers the Pinterest share option.

--------------------------------

fn_post_thumbnail.php
	Contains two functions which grab a thumbnail image for the post. It looks for (in this order): featured image, custom image (if the post type is a Page and there is a custom field called "custom_image_value"), first attached image, first image in the content, or a default image you set as a CONSTANT in functions.php

--------------------------------

functions.php
	Contains functions used by the included files. Add these to your functions.php file.

--------------------------------

add-this-share-options.php
	Original snippet from the AddThis site. Some customization is included: custom Twitter handle, Pinterest. No tooltip.

--------------------------------

inc-sharebox-images.php
	Custom snippet with five share options. Icon image files directly referenced; no text for share option. Tooltip js included.

--------------------------------

inc-sharebox-text.php
	Custom snippet with five share options. Text label for each share option wrapped in SPAN tag. Icons added via css. Tooltip js included.

--------------------------------

styles.css
	Styles for sharebox id, tooltip, icons.
